<para> </para><itemizedlist mark="bullet" spacing="compact"><listitem>Unix Single-Tier users pass the following values in your ODBC-JDBC Bridge Data Source:*</listitem>
</itemizedlist><itemizedlist mark="bullet" spacing="compact"><listitem>Name - Any Descriptive Title </listitem>
<listitem>Database Name - JDBC Driver Name String <programlisting>openlink.jdbc3.Driver 
</programlisting> </listitem>
<listitem>Options - Functional JDBC connection URL.
