</programlisting> </listitem>
<listitem>Username - JDBC Data Source Userid </listitem>
<listitem>Existing Environment - Pass the value that corresponds to your JRE version: JDBC 1.1, JDBC 1.2, JDBC 1.3, or JDBC 1.4.
</listitem>
<listitem>Windows Single-Tier users pass the following values in your ODBC-JDBC Bridge Data Source:*</listitem>
</itemizedlist><itemizedlist mark="bullet" spacing="compact"><listitem>Data Source Name - Any Descriptive Title </listitem>
