<programlisting>jdbc:openlink://localhost:5000/SVT=Oracle 8.1.x/DATABASE=ORCL/UID=scott/PWD=tiger 
</programlisting> </listitem>
<listitem>Multi-Tier users pass the following values in your ODBC-JDBC Bridge Data Source Names:*</listitem>
